ht:500;--framer-line-height:1.8em" class="framer-text">I conducted market research of current resale solutions to identify gaps in the market. While these platforms <strong class="framer-text">offer convenience</strong> for listing items, they often have <strong class="framer-text">unpredictable selling times</strong> and <strong class="framer-text">lack a sustainability focus</strong>. Most rely on users’ individual efforts to manage listings and transactions, which can be time-consuming and inefficient, especially for students with limited time to offload items before moving.</p></div></div><div class="framer-13i3alq" data-framer-name="Image" name="Image"><div style="position:absolute;border-radius:inherit;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0" data-framer-background-image-wrapper="true"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" sizes="(min-width: 1600px) 70vw, (max-width: 1599px) 70vw" srcset="https://framerusercontent.com/images/wwUOlnAc5CHYsnCSCwmOeYonQjs.png?scale-down-to=512 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/wwUOlnAc5CHYsnCSCwmOeYonQjs.png?scale-down-to=1024 1024w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/wwUOlnAc5CHYsnCSCwmOeYonQjs.png?scale-down-to=2048 2048w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/wwUOlnAc5CHYsnCSCwmOeYonQjs.png?scale-down-to=4096 4096w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/wwUOlnAc5CHYsnCSCwmOeYonQjs.png 7360w" src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/wwUOlnAc5CHYsnCSCwmOeYonQjs.png?scale-down-to=1024" alt style="display:block;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:inherit;object-position:center top;object-fit:contain" data-framer-original-sizes="70vw"></div></div><div class="framer-ts119d" style="outline:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-start;flex-shrink:0;transform:none" data-framer-component-type="RichTextContainer"><p style="--font-selector:R0Y7T3BlbiBTYW5zLTUwMA==;--framer-font-family:&quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Open Sans Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;--framer-font-weight:500;--framer-line-height:1.8em" class="framer-te